This website is programmed with python and the web framework tornado 4.1

It's juste an exemple of website build with tornado, you can modify it if you want.

For the dropdown menu the website use superfish: http://users.tpg.com.au/j_birch/plugins/superfish/
For the design the website use Foundation 5: http://foundation.zurb.com/

I create it with Debian wheezy and necessary packets are :

The recommended Python version is 2.7 : sudo apt-get install python.

Download and install pip at https://pip.pypa.io/en/latest/installing.html

Install tornado with : sudo pip install tornado.

Install email with : sudo pip install email.

Launch the website with : python main.py.

Create a mandrill account at http://mandrill.com/ or use an other SMTP service.
Modify main.py and add your mandrill account and API KEY for SMTP automatic mail service.

